{"tid":96901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"親戚？我親你老母戚","createTime":"2017-01-27T08:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T04:37:40.000Z","uid":64409,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a74e148599528d229918377666080f5a737f1932","tid":96901,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:46:39.000Z","msg":"朋友A住私樓 之前新年初五初六<br />\n上佢屋企玩 一開始冇諗住攞利是<br />\n朋友A老豆比左兩封利是比我地 <br />\n我同朋友B 就一人兩封 一封$20 一封$50 <br />\n非常得體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使兩封$20我都覺得人之常情 <br />\n大家初見面就過兩封利是黎<br />\n<br />\n親戚果便 表哥同表嫂加埋月入十幾萬<br />\n年年都兩封廿蚊 一開始我都習以為常<br />\n<br />\n直到去朋友A屋企既時候先醒覺 <br />\n朋友A直言平時都係兩封廿蚊封比看更<br />\n<br />\n果下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位 利是係一份心意 <br />\n但同時都係對人嘅尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家新年快樂 財源滾滾 萬事如意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710b254c508c4e1d7aeba1bfb8ee42018bf7cb46","tid":96901,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1a425282a7db10d90d4ffebe2d86fdf25ef7248","tid":96901,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"屌 封得少又要比你屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76376fe7e5fb85efae3225f43e403750171a9f1","tid":96901,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"封比我少唔緊要<br />\n但係人地封番咁多比你果時唔好屌鬼就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n最撚憎親戚永遠年年唔回禮<br />\n年年送把撚呀？<br />\n一年半年唔送又會話你地唔識做<br />\n<br />\n所以幾時都話。唔係個個長輩都值得尊敬"},{"pid":"146bbcb011180639d8ed8e86743b36024ced23ca","tid":96901,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>封比我少唔緊要<br />\n但係人地封番咁多比你果時唔好屌鬼就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n最撚憎親戚永遠年年唔回禮<br />\n年年送把撚呀？<br />\n一年半年唔送又會話你地唔識做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 所以幾時都話。唔係個個長輩都值得尊敬</span></blockquote><br />\n依個真 啲仆街親戚真係由鳩佢仆街由鳩佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4a4f173e9f3ac5864a1ba8170c9aaeebbfbe3d","tid":96901,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我而言，封1蚊就夠，都係意頭野啫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980b2ab83b0d5695542f9203e44745d48e36402","tid":96901,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我而言，封1蚊就夠，都係意頭野啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一毫都係錢 收到你咩感受先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c7da8b64c09bda1baa7d355d1d9506e778b5f8","tid":96901,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>封比我少唔緊要<br />\n但係人地封番咁多比你果時唔好屌鬼就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n最撚憎親戚永遠年年唔回禮<br />\n年年送把撚呀？<br />\n一年半年唔送又會話你地唔識做<br />\n<br />\n所以幾時都話。唔係個個長輩都值得尊敬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我遲下封撚返啲散紙比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01a055e6f237d1438cead2f80a5874fbc0193d9","tid":96901,"uid":1579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我而言，封1蚊就夠，都係意頭野啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一蚊果d唔係利是喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f971d1206e2699c9d491eac90992f133cd4049a8","tid":96901,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁點解你要人封咁多比你先<br />\n你值呢個價？"},{"pid":"f72e70423710fe2ea886738be5fc42b56ba94508","tid":96901,"uid":71725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:12:32.000Z","m